HWACOM SYSTEMS I said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 43.90% to NT$127,628,000 from NT$227,505,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales            127,628          227,505    
YOY%             -43.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            694,354          903,163    
YOY%             -23.12% 
=================================================================
 